		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.04]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>some other tricks i use:<br><br>1. using walls with casters mobs. <br><br>IE run behind a wall ( easy to find a wall in dungeon ) <br>wait first casting <br>you know then that the mob will need to have you in sight before re casting on you.. so FD after 1st cast. <br><br>Handy to split caster / warrior mobs.<br><br><br>2. 2 mnks pulling.<br>i'm playing a lot the back puller. It means FDing on a safe spot far enough from the group while the main puller pulls. If main puller bring like 6 7 mobs on my fd spot, i watch an occasion to pull one.( IE RZ raid, how to split boss from the 7 8 fake boss ) .<br>PS : i'm lazy so i dont mind fding all the time and sometimes saying to raid / group inc bad moffo ;p. <br><br><br>3. ping pong FD.<br>You got 2 mobs... agro one enough so he follows you, let the tank agro the other one, then flee far from the group.<br>FD... naturally the mob will come back to the group. wait FD refresh, wake up. if the mob did not forgot you he will run to you ( it is rare he will forget you if you dmged him ;p ). so you ping pong the add with the group.<br><br><br>4 bioluminescent orb.<br>hell this one is quite dangerous to use and works like 40% of the time. And not on all mobs.<br>The effect of bio orb is to blind mobs . mob is blind, it means mob will attack nearest player. But if no player is near the mob will turn his back and flee. <br>2 mobs, you use bio orb on the first, the first mob will flee, the second mob will follow you to camp.<br>FD. <br>and voila.<br><br>Point is that in dungeons the blind mob will run randomly in the dungeon and will bring friends with him. nice way to start a train too. ( so be sure to have the msg your ennemies has forgotten you if you are not sure ) .<br><br>Cherub.<br><br>PS: nice post here, really complete, i like it. <br><br><i><span class=sm>Edited, Mon Jun 21 16:56:17 2004 by Gaellian</span class=sm></i></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td class=mhback align=right><span class=mh id=fs8><a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=3><img src=/shared/root_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Up" width=17 height=11> Thread Index</a> |  <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=3&post=1><img src=/shared/new_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="New" width=17 height=11> New Subject</a> | <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=3&mid=97067092513411&num=2&page=&post=1&mid=97067092513411><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply" width=17 height=11> Reply to Thread</a></span></td></tr><tr><td><table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 class=mform><tr><td colspan=1  style='font-size: 9.5px;'>2 Posts [ <a href="/fsearch.html?base=class3">Search Forums</a> ]</nobr></td></tr></table>&nbsp;</td></tr>
